(7131, 1, '<p>Post  a question, attend a meetup, share ideas or mentor people. With hundreds of  active users, the collective intelligence of these groups is ready to take on  the next wave of innovation. </p>\r\n<h5><strong>Customer Acquisition and Growth  Functions</strong></h5>\r\n<p>The  groups within growth functions will help you define your companys growth plan,  coordinate growth programs, create strategies for customer acquisitions and  optimize revenue funnels in collaboration with R&D and sales and marketing  leaders.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Research and Development</strong>  Focus on providing  innovative solutions for the future by collaborating or sharing ideas. <br>\r\n  <strong>Marketing</strong>  Whether youre an entrepreneur,  founder or growth hacker, this group is for you to learn, share and grow your  marketing solutions.<br>\r\n  <strong>Sales Management</strong>  Stay on top of your  game by learning the latest techniques, networking, and sharing sales related best  practices with professionals. </p>\r\n<h5><strong>Customer Value Delivery and  Operations Functions</strong></h5>\r\n<p>Collaborate  with manufacturing, supply chain and service managers to gain insights into an  end-to-end approach to operations guided primarily by the consumer perspective  and see which products or services truly drive your competitive advantage.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Service Management</strong>  Engage with the  community of service managers, executives, and leaders in the industry to  overcome challenges and share best practices.<br>\r\n  <strong>Manufacturing</strong>  This group connects  decision-makers from all types of manufacturing businesses and offers insights into  how you can put new techniques and practices to use in your company.<br>\r\n<strong>Supply Chain</strong>  Keep up to date on the  latest trends and issues in the supply chain and leverage innovative insights  from the leaders.</p>\r\n<h5><strong>Customer Value Enablement Functions</strong></h5>\r\n<p>Learn from  F&A, legal, procurement and HR to recognize gaps in processes to boost the  value provided to your customers.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Finance and Accounting</strong> - Seek answers to financial issues affecting  your company and network with peers in the business community.<br>\r\n  <strong>Legal</strong>  Find out what is happening in the  legal community around the world and connect with legal professionals for  insights into contemporary legal matters.<br>\r\n  <strong>Procurement</strong>  Transform procurement  into a critical business driver for your organization with the latest insights  from our network.<br>\r\n<strong>Human Capital</strong> - Join the network of the  new generation of HR leaders, develop your skills, contribute to discussions,  and more.</p>\r\n<h5><strong>Leadership Functions</strong></h5>\r\n<p>Stay on  top of your leadership game to help your business achieve its goals by  collaborating with the brightest minds.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Boards & CEO</strong>  Be inspired to drive  the change to take your business to the next level by sharing and learning from  the leaders.<br>\r\n<strong>CIO</strong>  Develop your leadership skills  with CIO leaders offering advice and tips to deliver change.</p>\r\n<h5><strong>CADS</strong></h5>\r\n<p>Build a  competitive advantage and identify new business opportunities in Cloud,  Analytics, Digital and security by networking with leaders  that are on top of their digital transformation journey.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cloud</strong>  Get the latest insights around  cloud strategy, cloud computing, share tips, and connect with peers around the  globe.<br>\r\n  <strong>Analytics</strong>  Have great discussions on all  things analytics, add value to your learning curve and expand your connections  in the industry.<br>\r\n  <strong>Digital</strong>  Leverage the power of a global, digitally  connected network to scale your business with tips from members.<br>\r\n<strong>Security</strong>  Remove barriers for your customers  and grow your business by being a part of a group that connects security  professionals.</p>\r\n'),
