(606, 'sys_about', 1, 'custom', '', '_sys_block_type_raw_1547020733', 13, 2147483647, '0', 'raw', '<div class=\"bx-page-about\">\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-about-block1\">\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-about-header\">\r\n  <p>As the leader of an organization, CEOs and C-Suite executives need to respond  to digital age challenges and develop leadership skills to build organization  culture that fosters and accelerates digital transformation. \r\n  So, what steps do  you need to take <br>to drive digital transformation?</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n  Trasers+ is a true  business-to-business collaborative networking platform for leaders and decision  makers aimed at reinventing transformation by fostering a collaborative  dialogue, promoting out-of-the-box thinking, and leadership development and  mutual support. Our forum enables the members to exchange leading edge insights  and practices on latest technologies, industry trends and innovative ideas in a  non-competitive environment. </p>\r\n<p>  Trasers+ offers you  an opportunity to interact, engage and build lasting relationships with hundreds  of like-minded leaders from a range of industries and share the experiences of your  digital transformation journey.  </p>\r\n<p>Trasers+ is an  invitation only membership platform and accepts membership from Directors and  above who are committed to driving digital transformation. No matter where you  are on your digital transformation journey, visit Trasers+ and discover why it  is your go to place to thrive and succeed in the digitally transformative  world. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-about-block2\">\r\n<h3>Why Join Trasers+</h3>\r\n<p>  Whether youve  built your company from ground up, taken it to new heights through a  transformation or gearing up for the start-up grind, youve already made a  mark. But youre hungry for more </p>\r\n<p>Trasers+, a  community of transformation leaders at the top and like-minded decision makers  offers you all of that  a strong foundation, a trusted peer group, wisdom and  inspiration. You will get a chance to interact with other leaders in  transformation industry, share your story, opinions and problems. The credits  earned through your participation can be converted into benefits such as access  to all groups and Trasers exclusive insights and reports. </p>\r\n<p>Look at what Trasers+  membership can mean to your professional journey.</p>\r\n<ul class=\"bx-page-about-join\">\r\n  <li><strong>Build your network</strong><br>\r\n    Networking is the  key to everything. Networking on Trasers+ will not only give you exposure to  new perspectives, but also access to stories and insights shared by other  transformation leaders. Join Trasers+ to develop relationships with the right  entrepreneur, right marketer and right technologist that would be instrumental  in helping you grow your business. </li>\r\n  <li><strong>Grow your business </strong><br>\r\n    Apple took 42  years to become the worlds first trillion-dollar company while Pinterest took  just 2.46 years to reach $1 billion. Whatever your business is, every great  idea seems implausible at first. Trasers+ community will provide that  much-needed insights to transform your seemingly far-fetched idea into a  breakthrough one. Learn hacks to raise  money, manage cash flow or build sales channels to take your company to the  next level. </li>\r\n  <li><strong>Learn from the experts</strong><br>\r\n    Have you ever  found yourself bogged down due to management or business challenges? At  Trasers+, you will find a group of mentors who will help you achieve high  growth by offering innovative solutions to complex problems. Our  knowledge-sharing community is at your disposal to help you at every step of  the way and focused on your success.</li>\r\n  <li> <strong>Build online reputation</strong><br>\r\n    It will get your  and your companys name out there. Frequent interactions with the community  will help you build your online reputation and trusted connections. Your  participation will help you earn credits that can be converted into benefits in  form of access to all groups, exclusive insights and reports, and options to  upgrade from amateur to pro.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-about-block3\">\r\n<h3>What else can you do on  Trasers+</h3>\r\n<p>Transforming  organizations require articulated aspirations, as well as the ability to  generate new ideas, collaborate, and learn from the constant churn. Trasers+  offers you a medium to do all this and more. Your contribution and  participation will help you earn credits that can be converted into benefits in  form of access to all groups, exclusive insights and reports, and options to  upgrade from amateur to pro.</p>\r\n<ul  class=\"bx-page-about-else\">\r\n  <li> <strong>Spot that roadblock</strong><br>\r\n    Have you wondered  why few companies fail to unleash their full potential? Its because they fail  to identify the barriers holding innovation back. Spur your business growth by  sharing your problems with like-minded transformation leaders and getting  solutions.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Let your creative juices flow</strong><br>\r\n    Have your freely  shared that one cool idea you got one night from churning around those abstract  brainstorms for critical transformation challenges? Here, you can share your  radical ideas and develop it further with the expertise of Trasers+ members. </li>\r\n  <li><strong>Share your story</strong><br>\r\n    Have you ever  driven radical change in your organization? Share your success story on  Trasers+ and inspire the community. Be the change you wish to see. </li>\r\n  <li><strong>Become a mentor </strong><br>\r\n    Nothing is ever  perfect, but constant improvements can take an innovative idea to  near-perfection. Do you have the drive to help individuals make things better?  Comment, ask, collaborate; make your contributions matter. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n  </div>  </div>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 4),
